          }
        }
      ],
      "data": {
        "markdown": "# Workflow / Execution Template\n\nCanonical v1 execution loop:\n- begin at a `trigger`\n- declare an `input`\n- perform an `action`\n- evaluate a `condition`\n- route through a `branch`\n- emit an `output`\n\nThe bridge row below is the authoritative class surface for this template.",
